<br>
In my haste, I made a mistake, and thankfully only lost 50pp.  Its kind of a neat trinkit item if you are into collecting those kinds of things, its a 2hs that can be equipped by casters, its kinda cute.  I did turn around and put it back up for sale at the cost I spent it for.  And it was purchased.  Later in a search I noticed that 2 of the same scythes were for sale for around 500pp each.   I think either people like me don't know that this IS NOT the pestilence scythe used in the Aegis of Life quest or some people are trying to run a scam.<br>
<br>
When you camp Lord Grimrot for the Aegis of Life quest, you must kill two versions of him.. Each version drops a pesticence scythe.  However only one is used in the quest.  On other servers its easy to tell them apart, since the one used in the quest is no drop.  However on FV since its not no drop its a bit trickier to figure out.<br>
<br>
Anyway, this is the scythe that I have seen in the bazaar for 500pp THIS IS NOT THE SCYTHE USED IN THE QUEST.<br>
Pestilence Scythe Submitted by: Scavy Willowleaf  <br>
LORE ITEM  <br>
Damage: 10<br>
Delay: 50 <br>
Ratio: 5 Below Average <br>
 <br>
Weight: 11.9 <br>
Weapon Skill: Two Hand Slash <br>
Classes: Necromancer Ranger Shaman Druid Paladin Shadowknight Bard Monk Rogue Warrior Beastlord  <br>
Races: All Races  <br>
Inventory Slot: Primary Melee <br>
 <br>
The one that is used in the quest is this one.  Minus the no drop flag<br>
<br>
Pestilence Scythe<br>
MAGIC ITEM  LORE ITEM  NO DROP<br>
Skill: 2HS   Atk Delay: 48<br>
DMG: 16   WT: 9.9   Dmg/Sec: 6.88<br>
SV POISON+10  SV DISEASE+10  <br>
Effect: Vampiric Curse<br>
Class: NEC SHD WAR <br>
Race: ALL <br>
<br>
So please be aware, if you're impatient like me and hate long camps that you may be purchasing the wrong item, and get stuck with junk for 500pp.<br>
<br>
Gayana Mederi<br>
38th Priestess of Rodcet Nife<br>
